502
01:02:39,447 --> 01:02:45,366
One after another,
God may give you luck.

503
01:02:45,367 --> 01:02:51,367
That's it, only fair.

504
01:03:16,127 --> 01:03:20,846
Bosnian, come back.

505
01:03:20,847 --> 01:03:26,847
Stand on the chair.

506
