he won't build a house,
he won't get married.

511
01:05:14,367 --> 01:05:19,806
Give him the money,
let him be damned.

512
01:05:19,807 --> 01:05:24,926
When you return to Ljubljana,
take your sister.

513
01:05:24,927 --> 01:05:27,886
Do you understand?

514
01:05:27,887 --> 01:05:32,126
