522
01:08:41,247 --> 01:08:43,486
One can cross himself from the astonishment.

523
01:08:43,487 --> 01:08:48,526
If you were here, you could not get a wink
from the happiness.

524
01:08:48,527 --> 01:08:51,206
Unlce Ahmed
used to nicely tell you:

525
01:08:51,207 --> 01:08:53,646
We could have a 
sack of money.

526
01:08:53,647 --> 01:08:55,566
This isn't important now.

527
01:08:55,567 --> 01:08:58,766
Take care of my Azra,
so she doesn't end like the neighbour,

528
01:08:58,767 --> 01:09:00,966
whose feet wondered 
more in the sky,

529
01:09:00,967 --> 01:09:06,967
then stepped on the earth.

530
01:09:10,807 --> 01:09:12,606
My Hatidza!

531
01:09:12,607 --> 01:09:16,166
I have realised here that God,
is not a blind cat.

532
01:09:16,167 --> 01:09:19,046
Ahmed is like a father to me.

533
01:09:19,047 --> 01:09:21,686
He speaks Italian,
barks at the stars.

534
01:09:21,687 --> 01:09:23,486
He has his people everywhere,

535
01:09:23,487 --> 01:09:28,246
lawyers, judges,
priests and cops.

536
01:09:28,247 --> 01:09:31,286
He takes care of me like I was his son.

537
01:09:31,287 --> 01:09:35,326
I will earn a lof of money. I'll 
build a house, just like Ahmed's.

538
01:09:35,327 --> 01:09:37,966
Only I'll build according to
an italian plan.

539
01:09:37,967 --> 01:09:41,726
A painter will paint this
picture on the frontage.

540
01:09:41,727 --> 01:09:43,846
Don't worry about Danira.

541
01:09:43,847 --> 01:09:47,806
I've seen with my own eyes
that the doctor is Ahmed's man.

542
01:09:47,807 --> 01:09:51,286
What should I buy you?
I've bought uncle a TV.

543
01:09:51,287 --> 01:09:54,566
He can put it in his pocket,
let the whole world stand openmouthed.

544
01:09:54,567 --> 01:10:00,567
Latest technological advancement.

545
01:10:03,127 --> 01:10:06,126
I won't spare with the money
for the wedding.

546
01:10:06,127 --> 01:10:10,646
Let the old and the young remember
Perhan's wedding.

547
01:10:10,647 --> 01:10:16,647
Yours, Perhan.

548
01:10:32,767 --> 01:10:35,926
Where is Irfan?

549
01:10:35,927 --> 01:10:41,927
Where is Irfan, you nitwit?
- I don't know.

550
01:10:50,487 --> 01:10:54,726
