551
01:10:54,727 --> 01:10:58,126
Why didn't you pay attention?

552
01:10:58,127 --> 01:11:01,886
Don't appear before my eyes
without him!

553
01:11:01,887 --> 01:11:05,766
Out! Don't come
without him.

554
01:11:05,767 --> 01:11:11,767
