- Be off with you! Your problem!

555
01:11:47,567 --> 01:11:50,606
That's nothing.

556
01:11:50,607 --> 01:11:56,607
Tears? Oh my, mommy,
that's not good.

557
01:11:56,927 --> 01:11:59,966
What's missing in 
your full house?

558
01:11:59,967 --> 01:12:05,967
Tell me please,
what!

559
01:12:09,087 --> 01:12:14,726
Take the white coffee,
white bread, white cheese.

560
01:12:14,727 --> 01:12:20,727
Take the marmelade,
bird's milk. Everything that I have.

561
01:12:22,527 --> 01:12:28,527
You want a leave, to go on sick leave?
