581
01:18:53,487 --> 01:18:56,886
Everybody out!
Everybody to the police!

582
01:18:56,887 --> 01:19:02,887
Let's go!

583
01:19:34,487 --> 01:19:37,006
All to the police!

584
01:19:37,007 --> 01:19:43,007
They will take your passport.
